title: Location, Community, Quality Living. It Starts Here!
posting_body: ['The Vineyards Apartments', '7936 Westwood Drive, Gilroy, CA, 95020', 'Call Now', 'show contact info', 'Call for Availability!!!', 'FLOOR PLANS - please call for availability', '- ONE BEDROOM', '- TWO BEDROOM TWO BATH', '- TWO BEDROOM TWO BATH WITH A LOFT', '- TWO BEDROOM TWO BATH TOWN HOMES', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES.', 'Surround yourself with luxury at The Vineyards Apartments.', 'Discover the boutique wineries of the Gilroy Wine Trail and local festivals that make our community unique while enjoying the convenience and privacy of our apartment community.', 'Schedule a tour today!', 'PET FRIENDLY.', 'We allow cat and (dog with weight limit) maximum of 2 pets.', '- Pet deposit: (1 pet) $500.00 (2 pets) $750.00', '- Pet monthly fees: Dog $75.00, Cat $50.00', 'APARTMENT FEATURES:', '- Dishwasher', '- Washer & dryer in the unit', '- Central air conditioning & heating', '- Plank flooring & carpet in the bedroom', '- Garbage disposal', '- Balcony or patio', '- White appliances', 'AMENITIES:', '- Reserved/Assigned carport', '- Shared garage', '- Fitness center', '- Seasonal Pool', '- Spa open all year', '- Playground', '- Picnic area', 'RENTAL APPLICATION REQUIREMENTS', '- Applicant 18 years of age and above must fill out an application', '- Gross monthly income must be 2.5 times the rent', '- Security deposit:', 'One Bedroom $800, Two Bedroom $900, Two Bedroom Town Home $1,000']
